<h3>Reservation Policy</h3>
We require a credit card number or gift certificate number to reserve an appointment.
<p>
We kindly request 24 hours notice on scheduling, rescheduling, or cancelling appointments.  If a 24-hour notice is not given for cancellations or rescheduling (with the exception of emergency situations) a full charge will be applied.

<h3>Late Policy</h3>
If you are late for an appointment, a modified service will be performed
if time permits and will end at the scheduled time. However,
if time does not permit, you will be charged 50% of the services selected.
